- Weapon.

1828
01:07:28,617 --> 01:07:29,956
- The cutting-edge weapon.
- Weapon.

1829
01:07:29,957 --> 01:07:31,116
- Technology.
- Technology.

1830
01:07:31,117 --> 01:07:32,117
- Technology.
